waiting for us to come back.

526
00:50:53,592 --> 00:50:55,845
Nothing to do but cut and run, huh?

527
00:50:56,720 --> 00:50:58,313
Eh, what else?

528
00:50:58,681 --> 00:51:02,686
What about the old American
social custom of self-defense?

529
