have dubbed "The Vigilante."

574
00:56:41,106 --> 00:56:42,779
This will be
the first official statement...

575
00:56:42,941 --> 00:56:45,160
from Commissioner Dryer
on the Vigilante killings.

576
00:56:45,319 --> 00:56:47,663
I can see the commissioner now
as he walks past...

577
00:56:47,821 --> 00:56:52,201
