<i>of many people in our city...</i>

586
00:57:24,191 --> 00:57:26,068
<i>and I wanna say to our citizens:</i>

587
00:57:27,152 --> 00:57:31,282
<i>Murder is no answer
to crime in this city.</i>

588
00:57:31,448 --> 00:57:34,122
<i>Crime is a police responsibility...</i>

589
00:57:35,369 --> 00:57:38,248
<i>and if this person
is listening to my voice...</i>

590
00:57:39,081 --> 00:57:42,210
<i>I urge him
in the name of law and order...</i>

591
00:57:43,335 --> 00:57:48,557
<i>to desist from this one-man crusade
and turn himself in to the police.</i>

592
00:57:49,508 --> 00:57:52,227
<i>He'll be given fair treatment.</i>

593
00:57:52,386 --> 00:57:54,480
How do you like it?
That's our police commissioner...

594
