that's Ryder, the
king of clichés.

595
00:57:56,765 --> 00:57:59,439
<i>- vigilante's identification?
- No comment at this time.</i>

596
00:57:59,643 --> 00:58:02,271
<i>Do you think this man's crazy?</i>

597
00:58:02,562 --> 00:58:05,111
<i>Well, he's got a wire down, all right...</i>

598
00:58:05,315 --> 00:58:08,159
<i>but I don't believe we're
dealing with a raving maniac.</i>

599
00:58:08,360 --> 00:58:11,739
<i>Commissioner, it's rumored that
the rate of street muggings has dropped...</i>

600
00:58:11,905 --> 00:58:14,408
