All right.

612
00:58:50,444 --> 00:58:52,492
I'll put you through to Rosenberg.

613
00:58:52,654 --> 00:58:55,077
He's in charge of
confessions today.

614
00:58:55,574 --> 00:58:57,622
That's the 23rd.

615
00:58:57,951 --> 00:58:59,294
Put him through.

616
00:58:59,911 --> 00:59:03,131
We couldn't get any prints
off The Vigilante's groceries.

617
00:59:03,331 --> 00:59:06,881
- Wasn't there a sales slip?
- Yeah. Here.

618
00:59:08,587 --> 00:59:11,215
D'Agostino's.

619
00:59:11,673 --> 00:59:13,095
Mm-hm.

620
00:59:14,551 --> 00:59:18,351
Some of this code must identify
the particular store.

621
00:59:18,722 --> 00:59:20,395
Find out where it is.

622
00:59:20,640 --> 00:59:22,108
When we get the records...

623
00:59:22,267 --> 00:59:26,022
check on families that have had
somebody killed by muggers.

624
00:59:26,229 --> 00:59:29,699
Let's put them through the computer and
see if any of them live near this store.

625
00:59:31,443 --> 00:59:35,448
People are inclined to buy groceries
in their own neighborhoods.

626
00:59:36,698 --> 00:59:39,702
