689
01:06:50,924 --> 01:06:53,393
<i>One of the boys
up on the steel yelled down:</i>

690
01:06:53,551 --> 01:06:55,269
<i>"There's a mugging going on!"</i>

691
01:06:55,470 --> 01:06:59,395
<i>So we come out of the hole and through
